      user. The existing `HubSpot Integration Permissions` and `HubSpot Integration
      PermissionsV2` permsets handle the Zelis-side HubSpot grants; this atom
      complements them with MI-specific data access. Standalone is correct — there
      is no `Persona - System User HubSpot Integration` PSG today.
      Should NOT be assigned to: any human user.
    -->
    <description
  >Integration atom for the HubSpot inbound user posting Engagement_Touch__c via Apex REST. Full CRUD + viewAll/modifyAll on the four MI objects + class access on EngagementInboundRest and deps. Assign STANDALONE; not for humans. See source comment.</description>
